FBIS3-17103 "drsov056_p_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Mar 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Nation To Switch To Summer Time 27 Mar NC2303064494 Yerevan SNARK in English 1609 GMT 22 Mar 94 NC2303064494 Yerevan SNARK Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Yerevan, March 22 (SNARK) -- Armenia is also passing to summer time along with Russia. Armenian Government's press-service told SNARK hands of the clocks all over Armenia would be changed forward on a hour on March 27 night. Thus, there will be no difference in time between Moscow and Yerevan as before.
